      "body": "\"^Verse\"\nE ^F ^G/2 B/2 B/2 B/2 | E ^F ^G B |\nw: Chval- me Ho- spo- di- na vše- moc- né- ho,\nE ^F ^G/2 ^c/2 ^c/2 ^c/2 | E ^F ^G ^c |\nw: všich- ni, kdo ctí služ- bou jmé- no je- ho.\n^F ^G A/2 ^c/2 ^c/2 ^c/2 | ^F ^G A ^c |\nw: Ve všech kou- tech svě- ta, ve dne, v~no- ci,\nB ^G ^c ^G | B/2 B/2 ^G/2 ^G/2 ^c2 | ^G4 |\nw: slav- me vel- ké či- ny je- ho mo- ci.",
